milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (355) involving teams Canada & Afghanistan in ODIs
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Mohammad Nabi's 3
Asghar Afghan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for AFG, going past Mohammad Nabi

stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Canada, Sharjah, 2nd ODI
stories.seoTitle: Khurram Chohan leads Canada to victory
